translate chinese u20h_5aee407c:

    # "For now, I should go see Izzy."
    "眼下，我该去见伊兹了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20h.rpy:5
translate chinese u20h_72a90d54:

    # "I drive over to Izzy's house and knock on her door."
    "我开车来到伊兹家，敲了敲她的门。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20h.rpy:6
translate chinese u20h_a6bc8933:

    # "It's late, but she might still be awake. I need to see her."
    "虽然很晚了，但她可能还没睡。我必须见她。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20h.rpy:10
translate chinese u20h_9342f0d4:

    # "Izzy opens the door, her eyes wide with surprise and filling with tears."
    "伊兹打开门，惊讶得睁大了眼睛，眼眶里噙着泪水。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20h.rpy:11
translate chinese u20h_01dbc2b7:

    # gl "Holy shit, [pcname]!"
    gl "天啊，[pcname]！"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20h.rpy:14
translate chinese u20h_840b6638:

    # gl "Damn, I thought that machine killed you, Twig."
    gl "该死，我还以为那台机器把你给弄死了，特威格。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20h.rpy:15
translate chinese u20h_404faba8:

    # gl "I missed you so damn much."
    gl "我真的好想你。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20h.rpy:18
translate chinese u20h_d9c0289b:

    # gl "What happened? Did you see your dad?"
    gl "发生了什么？你见到你爸了吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20h.rpy:19
translate chinese u20h_0118c310:

    # pc "Yeah, I did. I'll tell you all about it tomorrow."
    pc "嗯，见到了。明天我再详细告诉你。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20h.rpy:22
translate chinese u20h_9051c62e:

    # gl "Alright then. I'm just glad you're back."
    gl "好吧。反正我很高兴你回来了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20h.rpy:23
translate chinese u20h_bd739f39:

    # gl "But your hair... damn. You gotta cut that shit."
    gl "不过你的头发……天啊。你得把那玩意儿剪短了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20h.rpy:24
translate chinese u20h_e7bdc60a:

    # pc "Yeah, yeah, I know."
    pc "是啊，是啊，我知道。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20h.rpy:27
translate chinese u20h_0f040bf1:

    # gl "Come on, let's go to my room."
    gl "来吧，去我房间。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20h.rpy:28
translate chinese u20h_e0cc24b1:

    # gl "We gotta be quiet, because the boys are here, but I'm gonna get me some of that dick tonight."
    gl "我们得小声点，因为那几个家伙在，但我今晚非得搞定那个家伙不可。"

